Licensed under the LGPL License (Lesser General Public License).  
The VOICEVOX engine is licensed under LGPL, which allows for broad use and distribution. However, if you modify the VOICEVOX engine itself, you are required to release the modifications under the same LGPL license.  
For more details, please see the VOICEVOX-engine license:  
https://github.com/VOICEVOX/voicevox_engine/blob/master/LGPL_LICENSE

